 * `Model::openai(options)` from the foreign-language side).
 * Once obtained, call [`complete`](Self::complete) (async) or
 * [`complete_blocking`](Self::complete_blocking) (sync) to generate
 * responses.
 */
public interface ModelInterface {
    /**
